SUMMARY:FREE HUD Approved In person Homebuyer workshop
LOCATION:13704 North 20th Street Tampa \, FL 33613 United States
DESCRIPTION:Your journey to homeownership starts here! Join us for our FRE
 E In-Person Homebuyers Workshop and learn everything you need to know abou
 t purchasing your first home\, improving your credit\, understanding the m
 ortgage process\, and accessing available down payment assistance programs
 . Up to 100\,000 in Down Payment Assistance may be available for qualified
  buyers! Harvest Hope Park Center 13704 North 20th Street\, Tampa\, FL 336
 13 Saturday\, June 13 8:30 AM  4:00 PM HUD-Approved Housing Counseling Age
 ncy Lunch will be provided Limited seats available  Registration is REQUIR
 ED! Take the first step toward building generational wealth and making you
 r dream of homeownership a reality. Register today at: www.reach4housing.o
